		quest.30F97EB743B0A07F.quest_desc: {
			new: ["Check out the Modules to learn more on how to use and upgrade the DE items! The Wyvern Axe is similar to Minecraft Axes after Combat Updates. They can designed off a weapon to slay foes, or a tool to chop down trees."]
