		quest.0000A88BB40B2149.quest_desc: {
			new: ["Now before you get to the Chaos Island I recommend preparing, he may look like the Ender Dragon but this one is much more difficult. You'll want Draconic Weapons or Tools that do a lot of damage as those will make it easier. He will also do a crap-ton of damage good Armor like Unobtainium or Meka-Suit will be recommeneded. (Also effects of Regeneration, Absorption, and Resistance will help you survive}. Don't worry you can always come back to fight another day if you aren't ready."]
			old: ["{atm9.quest.draconic.desc.prep}"]
		}
		quest.295EB6CFEC029AE2.quest_desc: {
			new: ["Before you get here first you need an item that needs OP in it: Wyvern Bow, Chaotic Capacitor, Staff of Power whatever. Then you need an Energy Module in the item, that determines the OP storage in the item and that's what the item will use to power up. Once you have that, make and place the Energy Transfuser, get OP in it, then place your item into it! You'll know it's working when the OP in it lights up and moves."]
			old: ["{atm9.quest.draconic.desc.transfuser}"]
		}
