		quest.45EE60207C466D6C.quest_desc: {
			new: ["To get into Draconic Evolution you'll need Chaos Shards. Chaos Shards are in Chaos Islands guarded by Chaos Guardians in the End. Go to the End at an X/Z coordinate that is a multiple of 10k. 10k, 10k / 10k, 20k / 20k, 20k etc."]
